---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import PolaroidGrid from '../components/PolaroidGrid.astro';
---
<PageLayout title="About">
  <h2 class="greeting">Hi, welcome to my site!</h2>

  <PolaroidGrid />

  <p>
    I'm Apurva from <strong>Houston, TX</strong>. I studied <strong>information science</strong> at the
    <a href="https://umich.edu">University of Michigan</a>. I'm a cloud engineer at
    <a href="https://aws.amazon.com">Amazon Web Services</a> working on enterprise VPC architecture,
    WAF, Route 53, and network infrastructure.
  </p>

  <p>
    Before AWS, I interned at Becht Engineering building analytics dashboards for refining and oilfield
    clients. At Michigan I led a team that took an IoT medication platform from napkin sketch to
    <a href="/projects">$15K in funding</a>.
  </p>

  <p>
    I just love <a href="/projects">building stuff</a>, whether that's cloud infrastructure tooling,
    ML models, or multi-agent systems. I read too much about wine and watch too much F1.
    Michigan football runs through my blood.
  </p>

  <p>
    Most days you'll find me skiing, golfing, or finding something new to add to
    <a href="https://beliapp.com">Beli</a>. There's so much I want to understand and countless
    problems worth solving. Thanks for stopping by and have fun exploring!
  </p>

  <div class="f1-tracks">
    <p class="track-label">Favorite circuits</p>
    <div class="track-row">
      <div class="track-item" title="Circuit de Monaco">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round">
          <path d="M50,15 L75,15 Q85,15 85,25 L85,45 Q85,55 75,55 L60,55 Q50,55 50,65 L50,75 Q50,85 40,85 L25,85 Q15,85 15,75 L15,35 Q15,25 25,25 L35,25 Q45,25 50,15Z"/>
        </svg>
        <span>Monaco</span>
      </div>
      <div class="track-item" title="Circuit of the Americas">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round">
          <path d="M20,80 L20,40 L30,20 L50,20 L60,30 L70,25 L80,30 L80,45 L65,50 L55,45 L50,50 L60,60 L75,55 L85,65 L80,80 L60,85 L40,75 L20,80Z"/>
        </svg>
        <span>COTA</span>
      </div>
      <div class="track-item" title="Suzuka International Racing Course">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round">
          <path d="M30,85 L15,70 L15,40 Q15,20 35,20 L65,20 Q85,20 85,40 L85,50 L70,55 L55,45 L40,55 L55,65 L70,60 L85,70 L85,80 Q85,90 70,85 L30,85Z"/>
        </svg>
        <span>Suzuka</span>
      </div>
      <div class="track-item" title="Autodromo Nazionale Monza">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round">
          <path d="M45,85 L25,70 Q15,60 20,45 L30,30 Q40,15 55,15 L65,20 Q80,25 80,40 L75,55 L65,60 L60,50 L65,40 L55,35 L40,45 L45,60 L55,70 L50,80 L45,85Z"/>
        </svg>
        <span>Monza</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h3>Elsewhere</h3>
  <ul class="elsewhere">
    <li><a href="https://github.com/ApurvaDesai6">GitHub</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://linkedin.com/in/-desai-apurva">LinkedIn</a></li>
    <li><a href="mailto:apurvad@umich.edu">Email</a></li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Website</h3>
  <p class="credits">
    Built with <a href="https://astro.build">Astro</a>. Hosted on AWS (S3 + CloudFront).
    Source on <a href="https://github.com/ApurvaDesai6/apurva-portfolio">GitHub</a>.
    Typeset in Fraunces, Source Sans 3 &amp; Crimson Pro.
  </p>
</PageLayout>

<style>
  .greeting {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .elsewhere {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .elsewhere li { margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
  .credits {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
  }
  .f1-tracks {
    margin: 2.5rem 0;
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  .track-label {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .track-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .track-item {
    text-align: center;
    cursor: default;
  }
  .track-item svg {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    transition: color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }
  .track-item:hover svg {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    transform: scale(1.1);
  }
  .track-item span {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin-top: 4px;
  }
</style>
